726120f-a.title: Queens: Baisley Boulevard - 167th Street
726120f-a.text:
Baisley Boulevard, at the N. E. Worner of 167th Street.
This colonial home was owned by one Balis in 1891. (See
Volverton's 1891 atlas of Cueens County, plate 28.)
P. L. Sperr  March 15, 1927
